\c 25
\s Mufananidzo wavasikana gumi
\p
\v 1 Panguva iyo ushe hwokumatenga huchafananidzwa nevasikana gumi vakatora marambi avo vakabuda kunochingamidza muwani.
\v 2 Zvino vashanu vavo vakange vakachenjera, vashanu \add vari\add* mapenzi.
\v 3 Avo vari mapenzi vakatora marambi avo, vakasatora mafuta pamwe navo.
\v 4 Asi vakachenjera vakatora mafuta mumidziyo yavo nemarambi avo.
\v 5 Zvino muwani wakati achinonoka, vese vakatsumwaira vakavata.
\v 6 Asi pakati pousiku kwakadanidzirwa: Tarirai, muwani ouya, budai munomuchingamidza!
\v 7 Zvino vasikana avo vese vakamuka, vakagadzira marambi avo.
\v 8 Mapenzi akati kuna vakachenjera: Tipei pamafuta enyu nekuti marambi edu odzima.
\v 9 Asi vakachenjera vakapindura vachiti: Zvimwe haangakwaniri isu nemwi; asi zviri nani endai kuna vanotengesa munozvitengera.
\v 10 Asi vakati vachienda kundotenga, muwani akasvika. Zvino vakange vakagadzirira vakapinda naye mumuchato, mukova ukapfigwa.
\v 11 Pashure kwakauyavo vamwe vasikana, vachiti: Ishe, Ishe, tizarurirei!
\v 12 Asi wakapindura akati: Zvirokwazvo ndinoti kwamuri: Handikuziviyi imwi.
\v 13 Naizvozvo rindai, nekuti hamuzivi zuva kana nguva Mwanakomana wemunhu yaachauya.
\s Mufananidzo wamatarenda*
\p
\v 14 Nekuti \add zvakaita\add* somunhu wakafamba rwendo, akadana varanda vake, akavapa zvaaiva nazvo.
\v 15 Uye kune umwe wakapa matarenda* mashanu, umwe maviri, umwe rimwe, umwe neumwe zvakakwanirana nesimba rake; pakarepo akafamba rwendo rwake.
\v 16 Uye wakagamuchira matarenda* mashanu akaenda akaita mhindu nawo, akaita mamwe matarenda mashanu.
\v 17 Saizvozvovo wemaviri akawanawo mamwe maviri.
\v 18 Asi wakagamuchira rimwe wakaenda akachera pasi, akaviga mari yashe wake.
\v 19 Shure kwenguva refu, ishe wavaranda ivavo akasvika, akagadzira zvemari navo.
\v 20 Kwakauya wakange agamuchira matarenda mashanu akauyisa mamwe matarenda mashanu achiti: Ishe, makandikumikidza matarenda mashanu; tarirai, ndawana pamusoro pawo mamwe matarenda mashanu.
\v 21 Ishe wake akati kwaari: Zvakanaka, muranda wakanaka, wakatendeka, wakange wakatendeka pazvishoma, ndichakuisa pamusoro pezvizhinji; pinda mumufaro washe wako.
\v 22 Wakange agamuchira matarenda maviri akauyavo akati: Ishe, makandikumikidza matarenda maviri; tarirai, ndawana mamwe matarenda maviri pamusoro pawo.
\v 23 Ishe wake akati kwaari: Zvakanaka, muranda wakanaka, wakatendeka, wakange wakatendeka pazvishoma, ndichakuisa pamusoro pezvizhinji; pinda mumufaro washe wako.
\v 24 Asi wakange agamuchira tarenda rimwe naiye wakauya akati: Ishe, ndakanga ndichikuzivai imwi kuti muri munhu wakawoma, munokohwa pamusina kudzvara, munounganidza pamusina kukusha;
\v 25 zvino ndakatya, ndikaenda ndikanoviga tarenda renyu muvhu; tarirai, mava nechenyu!
\v 26 Ishe wake akapindura akati kwaari: Muranda wakaipa unousimbe, wakange uchiziva kuti ndinokohwa pandisina kudzvara, ndichiunganidza pandisina kukusha.
\v 27 Saka waifanira kuisa mari yangu kuvatsinhanisi vemari, neni pakusvika ndingadai ndagamuchira zvangu nezvibereko.
\v 28 Naizvozvo mutorerei tarenda, mupe kune une matarenda anegumi.
\v 29 Nekuti wose unazvo uchapiwa ave nezvakawandisa; asi usina uchatorerwa nechaanacho.
\v 30 Nemuranda pasina murasirei kurima rekunze, ipapo pachava nekuchema nekugeda-geda kwemeno.
\s Kutonga kukuru
\p
\v 31 Zvino kana Mwanakomana wemunhu achiuya mukubwinya kwake, nevatumwa vatsvene vese vanaye, ipapo uchagara pachigaro choushe chekurumbidzwa kwake.
\v 32 Zvino pamberi pake pachaunganidzwa ndudzi dzose; uye uchadziparadzanisa imwe kubva kune imwe, somufudzi unoparadzanisa makwai kubva kumbudzi.
\v 33 Uchamisa makwai kuruoko rwake rwerudyi, asi mbudzi kuruboshwe.
\v 34 Zvino Mambo uchati kuna vari kuruoko rwake rwerudyi: Uyai, imwi makaropfadzwa naBaba vangu, mugare nhaka yeushe hwakagadzirirwa imwi kubva pakuvamba kwenyika.
\v 35 Nekuti ndakanga ndine nzara, mukandipa chokudya; ndakanga ndine nyota, mukandipa chokumwa; ndakanga ndiri mweni, mukandigamuchira;
\v 36 \add ndaka\add*shama, mukandipfekedza; ndakanga ndichirwara, mukandishanyira; ndakanga ndiri mutirongo, mukauya kwandiri.
\v 37 Ipapo vakarurama vachamupindura vachiti: Ishe, takakuonai rinhi mune nzara, tika\add ku\add*pai chokudya, kana mune nyota tikapa chokumwa?
\v 38 Takakuonai rinhi muri mweni, tikagamuchira, kana makashama, tikapfekedza?
\v 39 Takakuonai rinhi isu muchirwara, kana mutirongo, tikauya kwamuri?
\v 40 Uye Mambo uchapindura ati kwavari: Zvirokwazvo ndinoti kwamuri: Sezvamakaitira umwe wehama dzangu idzi mudukusa, makaitira ini.
\v 41 Ipapo uchatiwo kuna vari kuruoko rworuboshwe: Ibvai kwandiri, imwi makatukwa, \add muende\add* kumoto usingaperi, wakagadzirirwa Diaborosi nevatumwa vake.
\v 42 Nekuti ndakanga ndine nzara, mukasandipa chokudya; ndakanga ndine nyota, mukasandipa chokunwa;
\v 43 ndakanga ndiri mweni, mukasandigamuchira; ndakashama, mukasandipfekedza; ndichirwara, nemutirongo, mukasandishanyira.
\v 44 Ipapo ivava vachamupindurawo vachiti: Ishe, takakuonai rinhi mune nzara, kana mune nyota, kana muri mweni, kana makashama, kana muchirwara, kana muri mutirongo, tikasakushandirai?
\v 45 Zvino uchavapindura achiti: Zvirokwazvo ndinoti kwamuri: Pamusina kuitira umwe wavadukusa ava, hamuna kuitirawo ini.
\v 46 Ava vachaenda kukurangwa kusingaperi; asi vakarurama kuupenyu husingaperi.
